{"tid":315382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方大反黑掃場拘87人","createTime":"2017-07-10T03:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T06:38:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4538708ca87ca35c5bb08193461b205faf5c1fb3","tid":315382,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:42:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20084507&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20084507%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170710&d=SNSQihyh%2Fj3X1%2BENQWX1JU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ca913342\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20084507%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170710&h=19d75af6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20084507&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170710</a><br />\n<br />\n警方大反黑掃場拘87人<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方連日在全港展開「犁庭掃穴」反黑行動。有組織罪案及三合會調查科（O記），聯同五大總區反黑組、刑事偵緝部門及機動部隊，過去一連三天突擊搜查160多個地點，破獲多個賭檔、賣淫場所、無牌按摩院及黑幫武器庫，撿獲西瓜刀、伸縮警棍、鐵棍等武器。行動中警方拘捕82人，包括49男33女，年齡由18至77歲，部份有黑社會背景及持雙程證人士，涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器、經營非法賭檔、管理賣淫場所、管理無牌按摩院、藏毒及違反逗留條件等。<br />\n此外，西九龍總區反三合會行動組人員，前午於旺角砵蘭街316號一單位，撿獲海洛英、約60粒「藍精靈」毒品，拘捕一名44歲姓夏本地漢涉管理毒窟及販毒；另兩男兩女涉藏毒被捕。<br />\n■記者黎志偉、溫瑞麟<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\nO記連同各總區的反黑組探員展開犁庭掃穴行動，搜查全港多個娛樂場所。黎志偉攝"},{"pid":"18549b51632e7e2b76d51fd409919a97b37fc748","tid":315382,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170710/large/0709laicwimg_0008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170710%2Flarge%2F0709laicwimg_0008.jpg&h=d6ac142f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nO記連同各總區的反黑組探員展開犁庭掃穴行動，搜查全港多個娛樂場所。黎志偉攝"},{"pid":"707c70213c7aecb74631e2a94fc4340647f4f9a6","tid":315382,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f6998c9426e7f6be94bad0a877ba0a2c3ead500","tid":315382,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17c3e2bc7d4b01a10d551bd0893315cff69b9a5a","tid":315382,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bbacc7a6b3036ebcbec7bdfb2c45f694036d998","tid":315382,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"其實宜家仲多唔多開片<br />\n<br />\n成日搜到刀棍但又唔覺邊到有打過"},{"pid":"837301847bf526b8436bcda4aff200e4a64445e9","tid":315382,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實宜家仲多唔多開片<br />\n<br />\n成日搜到刀棍但又唔覺邊到有打過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n武器庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n武器庫得幾把刀仔,D黑幫幾陰公"},{"pid":"330bd4e95588831599f9dccc07f411c472492c86","tid":315382,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實宜家仲多唔多開片<br />\n<br />\n成日搜到刀棍但又唔覺邊到有打過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n武器庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n武器庫得幾把刀仔,D黑幫幾陰公</blockquote><br />\n你估拍戲有箱am手榴彈咩"},{"pid":"77f3974cf309802f739f8d91f2c2d3b4a9f16f6c","tid":315382,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>O記同反黑，邊個好打dm<